Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:05.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天比平時都要興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:08.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能是能在這麼寬敞的地方 很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.01,0:01:09.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.89,0:01:15.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:18.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:20.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:22.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}由我來拿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:24.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:29.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 趁我一不注意就想接近美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:31.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這垃圾蟲
