Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你說的是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:56.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}認真中的認真 非常認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:04:00.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪 你完全沒了解自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:04.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 看你過於在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:11.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}住嘴 我和原來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原來是 以後還是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:16.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一直這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:21.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:24.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一起在這喝茶怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:30.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 這家咖啡館真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:33.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔非常贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.30,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們看 小熊喵也能進去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
