Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:40.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:46.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:02.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 稍微有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 發生什麼事情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:32.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你居然不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:37.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 新吾現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.58,0:05:38.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都已經一個星期了吧 習慣新環境了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:44.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:47.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍微有點不太精神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:52.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 看來是對新環境還不太適應了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:55.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能是那樣的感覺

