Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:15.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算這麼說 也不能就放任不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡該輪到女僕出場了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:21.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之把現在不用的東西先收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:24.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就放在這個紙箱裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:28.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}賭上安潔的自尊 完美地整理好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我去把這個洗乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊等等 小紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:38.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:42.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 這裡就交給我們收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:44.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你去幫小紗凪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:48.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的 就這麼點事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:52.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還帶有石子 水箱也很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給我 讓我來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.77,0:06:56.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:07.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 好冰涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.69,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別說這麼沒出息的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:16.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算你這麼說 校舍裡也有可以出熱水的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:20.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在校舍裡 不能清洗這種會弄髒水槽的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偷偷洗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:26.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要認真遵守規則 這個是喵咪部的紀律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:32.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:34.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:45.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這傢伙 不僅是垃圾蟲 還是柔弱蟲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那真對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:12.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:17.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:22.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你莫非 就只有這麼一塊手帕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:27.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}之前借給你的也是這塊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:30.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你有清洗過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃有認真洗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我就用好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.95,0:08:48.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:49.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}裝太滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是箱子又只有這麼一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:57.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的 再過一會新吾就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:58.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}確實是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:02.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等主人回來以後 誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:07.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}向主人拜託這樣的事情 作為女僕有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放心吧 我會拜託他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:13.26,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.09,0:09:24.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個… 差不多可以還給我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:30.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要消毒過後再給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是清洗才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:36.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的 你看著就像養了奇怪的細菌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:38.06,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以要消毒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:39.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好的 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:40.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算是這樣吧

Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:47.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒…

Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:53.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 美羽精神也不太好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽也…嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 新吾也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:04.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}飯也不怎麼吃 一邊在屋裡亂轉一邊哭叫著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和飼主那裡聽說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}帶去醫院看了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:15.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 但是沒有發現生病或者有什麼異常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:20.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有就是那個… 有貓喜歡呆在家的說法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:25.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想著莫非是突然到了陌生的地方 變得有些混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就帶來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:31.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在找什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:36.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才就一直在房間裡轉圈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在找什麼東西嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:44.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:45.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:48.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽在找的是新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:54.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你 想見新吾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:56.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:00.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過對不起 新吾已經不在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:07.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然… 美羽必須和新吾在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:15.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽也由我來負責飼養
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪已經在養新吾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯 絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:26.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽只要和新吾在一起 就全部會恢復正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:27.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:28.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去把新吾帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:31.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:32.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…

Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:47.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.69,0:11:51.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:57.21,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你清楚嗎 新吾和美羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:12:00.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是喜歡的人的名字和情敵的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:06.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就想一直這樣生活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:12.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的… 不是情敵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:17.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩是值得我尊敬的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:22.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:28.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:42.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為這個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:56.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了 要是這樣也就只能如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:57.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然覺得很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:00.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都說沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起這個 萬智
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:07.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也養隻貓怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:08.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:10.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貓可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}古靈精怪隨心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:15.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然遇上不喜歡的事情馬上就逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:18.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一旦認定你了 那就已經是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:23.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你不是正好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身邊沒有男人 正好寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:26.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:43.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然沒有新吾在身邊 就不會去吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:44.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:49.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩 問你一件事可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:54.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:58.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼要反對紗凪養貓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪對貓會過敏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:05.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 櫻乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:11.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔們在這裡做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:12.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就沒有問的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:19.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:23.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡的打掃中午已經做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:27.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果那樣 還為什麼一直呆在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:34.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:40.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然說是過敏 但沒有嚴重到會馬上發作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:43.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果只是在這裡照顧的話 是沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:44.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果是在家裡養的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:52.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定是在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:54.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以就反對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:55.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:14:59.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:03.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我小時候 得過小兒哮喘所以知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:09.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能自由呼吸至幾近窒息 無法停止咳嗽的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:14.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算知道會這樣 那傢伙還…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:20.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太過勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:24.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩也 一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:24.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:31.25,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在我看來 你們兩個都為了動物而做出犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:35.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒想過那是犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果那樣的話 紗凪也是一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:44.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:48.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們都是那樣的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 可能是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這房間也變得寂靜多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:06.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢 那孩子下周也應該能回歸山林了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:11.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就只剩下小熊喵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:12.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:17.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總有一天 也想讓小熊喵回歸山林
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:24.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還沒有和新吾說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:28.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我和小熊喵初次相遇的事情

Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:39.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊

Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:49.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}覺得非常地怕生 像是不願和人類有所接觸的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:55.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後… 兩年前和小熊喵再次相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個時候的小熊喵 只剩下自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:03.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和現在相比 非常地柔弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:04.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}非常地膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:05.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不停地顫抖著

Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}夢中在向母親撒嬌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:18.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或者是 在和朋友們玩耍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:25.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放心吧 不久之後一定能和它們重逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:35.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小熊喵是脫離了群體的野生動物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以必須讓它回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就是 喵咪部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:53.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新…新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:10.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:15.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 突然間怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:20.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.93,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}突然間這麼說 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:39.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}選擇我可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:45.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾不是喜歡小紗凪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:49.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以… 都說那是誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:56.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:19:01.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 我喜歡的是美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有你一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:13.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:21.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果不介意這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:26.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯

Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:35.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…

Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:44.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被小熊喵給嚇壞了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}下雨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:06.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.17,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}努力讓我認可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:23.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為交換 我會叫你新吾的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:30.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:37.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你 喜歡美羽前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:19.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在做什麼呢 新吾會被淋濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:23.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:26.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:31.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是哭的話 男人是不會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:44.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只有今天 可以為那傢伙而哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}忘記他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:58.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那之前 你可以在我懷裡盡情哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:38.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也有喜歡的人嗎

